Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It all starts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Demon territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They deliberately let\Nthe Chaos run rampant on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way, settlements get fragmented,\Nand it's hard for people to band together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That type of ruling would never be allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the next step?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the town of Laxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rossini's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we go there,\Nwouldn't they know that we've arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phederico Rossini must've heard by now\Nthat you've declared to come to Sistina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll actually use the Rossini family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to spread the word all over Sistina\Nthat the hero, Theo Cornaro, has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To overthrow the Rossini family,\Nit's imperative that the people rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To make that happen, we'll start by\Nhaving you openly announce yourself in Laxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll reach out to every town\Non the island to apprehend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, they'll spread the word for us that\Nsomeone opposed to the Rossinis has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea it was thriving this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Irvin and Priscilla,\NI'd like you to go procure our supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Understood.\N-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca, why don't you\Nand the others go eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. We need to be conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jana, you truly are gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wretched...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just some people I met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, they really made me suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If those three are your enemy,\NI suppose I can't look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Salvador Rossini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can go ahead and tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Theo Cornaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? I see, so it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That there's someone reckless enough to try\Nto revolt against the Rossini family in Sistina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rossini. Mark my words, I'll defeat you,\Nand liberate the people of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This island is and will be ours, for all eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Rossini family,\NI order you to swear a blood oath of fealty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We have to run.\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who gather around\Nthe Omerta Flag become ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll carry out the most cruel act\Nwithout any remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then all we have to do is massacre them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to drag the townsfolk into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What was that?\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could you leave us behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had a hard time finding you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a search party patrolling the town.\NThere seems to be an Artist among them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, one of Rossini's Artists\Nwas that assassin who gave you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a blunder on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, what's that Black Witch from the\NForest of Eternal Darkness doing on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People with baggage flee to this island,\Nwhere they become the Rossini family's guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I think we've met our goal\Nof spreading the word of your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Almost too effectively, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here's the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tour the neighboring villages,\Nand call on the people to revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cornaro my foot, that wannabe hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, let me take care of him.\NI'll get rid of him for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like to hear!\NI'll bring you back Theo's head in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down, Salvador. It would be better\Nto gather the proper amount of troops first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You like to play it safe, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget, Salvador.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Execute extreme caution, and act boldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Rossini way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take down the Rossinis? Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd best leave this island\Nwhile you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that it won't be easy.\NBut I can't just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many of you are here?\NDid you bring along a large force?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, these are the only comrades I brought.\NI'd like the people of Sistina to rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's all the more impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You people can do whatever you want.\NBut we have no intention of helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you all abhor the Rossini family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who's resisted has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than stand up to them,\Nit's better to get on the Rossini's good side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people who feel that way,\Neven in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better watch out\Nso nobody snitches on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with them?\NDo they want things to stay the way they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that Sistina was ruled\Nwith fear and despair, but this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who swear a blood oath of fealty\Nto the Rossinis
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are given the right to plunder,\Nunder the guise of collecting taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So some try to become plunderers\Nto curry favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been like this ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who plunder,\Nand those who get plundered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They turn their citizens against each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and take their cut\Nwithout ever soiling their own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to realize how hard it's going to be\Nto defeat the Rossini family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that number too low for troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard about\Nany huge forces arriving on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other side has brought a skilled Shadow.\NPlease don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the one you failed to kill in Jalucia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's see you take him out.\NI'm giving you a chance to redeem yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salvador!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be away from the mansion for a while.\NI want you to wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Make sure you kill those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I have a good idea\Nwhere Theo's bound to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boltz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go send a warning to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show them what will happen\Nif they side with the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just because they suspected us\Nof sheltering you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they burned down the village to the north!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So many people have lost their homes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Sir Theo you should be blaming,\Nbut the Rossinis, who committed this outrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants you\Nto bring down the Rossini family!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of this village already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You're making trouble for us!\N- Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone at all on this island\Nwho will take Sir Theo's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? Wouldn't it be\Nuseless if we go to the next village?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about the village\Nwhere Sir Theo was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to Sir Theo's hometown,\Nthey might just welcome us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}All right. Let's head over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I want you to see the village\Nwhere I was born, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, think it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.\NThe villagers did a terrible thing to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they had to, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me they had no choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost all hope for this village,\Nand for Sistina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's under Rossini's thumb,\Nand they don't even feel bitter about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you gather everyone in the village?\NI want to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I couldn't bring myself\Nto forgive you all. That's why I left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what happened, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To elude the Rossini's plundering,\NTheo's father built a secret grain storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever food became scarce in the village,\Nhe would distribute it in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then someone in the village\Nsnitched on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They arrived here in droves,\Nand his father was handed over to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he was killed to set an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've put that behind me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father must've known it could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fine man, Theo.\NAnd so was your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing as I see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you just need to think about\Nwhat it is you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To continue living in fear of the Rossini family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or to put an end to that way of living?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's been a while,\Nwhy don't you visit your father's grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait for me here?\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've really made something of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you remember?\NThat day you left the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you went on\Nto become a Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, I always knew\Nthat you were different from the other boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find a way to defeat him.\NI'm certain of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did the Rossinis tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah.\N- Then why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I ran, who knew\Nwhat would've happened to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they might've been threatening you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you did it for the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one's threatening me. It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I managed to lure you,\NI made them promise to take me to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Rossinis, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Because it would be\Nbetter than living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you care?\NIt doesn't concern you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You left this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I just couldn't forgive the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I thought\Nit was their fault my father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But not anymore. It's the Rossini family\Nwho I should hate for ruling this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the citizens all rise up,\Nwe can defeat the Rossinis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came back here\Nso I could make an appeal to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's never going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, right? On this island,\Nno one survives if you stand up to the Rossinis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You're wrong about that!\N- I'm not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, Theo, they're going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true. Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, I want you to go back\Nand tell everyone to flee the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they hand me over, the Rossinis will\Nprobably make an example of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're all waiting for me\Nat Father's grave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I ran away from the village.\NBut I'm not running this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to fight them alone?\NThere's a lot of soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You're telling us that Theo\Nknowingly went along with Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Had Sir Theo turned her down, there's no telling\Nwhat they would've done to that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this village would've\Ncome under attack as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He did it to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Why would he do that?\N- Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because that is what a true Lord is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you see the Rossini family as your Lord,\Nthen go ahead and leave Sir Theo to his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you want to save Sir Theo,\Nthen take up your arms, and make a stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please help Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, unless we do something,\Nit'll be just like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You remember what happened after we\Nturned Theo's father over to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Far from rewarding us for our help,\Nthey hit us with heavy taxes as punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So will we turn in Theo this time?\NWill the same thing happen all over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really want to live like this forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca instructed me to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That man is the Shadow I mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a footman,\Nbut he's quite formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They may be highly skilled, but how much\Nwill it help to have three more on his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hearing footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo! Everybody decided to make a stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! The people of this island\Nwould never revolt against the Rossini family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the battle to bring an end\Nto the Rossini family's rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mere villagers\Nshouldn't get full of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let them find out what happens\Nto anyone who betrays the Rossini family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irvin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Sir Salvador!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salvador Rossini!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir Salvador...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat! We're withdrawing! Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She put her life on the line to stop Salvador.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allowing Salvador Rossini to get away\Nwould've been the same as losing this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO THE HOMELAND
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 14\NTHE LIBERATOR OF SISTINA
